room_title: Escape room "Alcatraz Prison Escape Room" by LI Escape Game in New York
room_description: There have been numerous attempts to escape from the Alcatraz prison but all of the inmates who dared to try were either killed or recaptured while others disappeared without a trace. Another escape plan is being prepared tonight, but you have to act fast. Will you be able to mastermind your way out of the notorious Alcatraz Penitentiary?
